ygData.subject: Re: Executioners Axe
ygData.msgSnippet: Aye they are green, and the corrupt guards will glower at you dubiously.  But if the good guards see you attacking the corrupt guards, well, lets just say
ygData.messageBody:
Aye they are green, and the corrupt guards
will glower at you dubiously. But if the good
guards see you attacking the corrupt guards,
well, lets just say hopefully you will have a
chance to gate <smiles>

Angarth, Clan Anstruther, Warrior of the 15th Tier
"Periissem ni periisem"
